These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
House: cottage, art-deco, palace, cape-cod, gothic-revival, modern
There are 6 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut, lavender, pink, black, orange
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the palace house##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
8. the person who likes black is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| House   | modern | cottage  | palace    | cape-cod  | art-deco      | gothic-revival    |
| Color      | chestnut  | orange | black | emerald | pink | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, april, february, september, june, january
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, black, amber, azure, turquise
1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Birthday   | may   | june | april | january | september     | february  |
| Color           | black | blood-red    | yellow      | turquise  | amber | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
There 6 different types of food: mango, grapefruit, grapes, strawberry, radish, pineapple
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, satire, mystery, western, superhero
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching satire movies is the person eating strawberry##1
9. the person eating grapes is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Food   | strawberry   | pineapple   | radish      | grapefruit | mango  | grapes   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | superhero | thriller | martial-arts   | western | mystery |

