.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, turtle, guinea-pig, snake, hedgehog
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, baseball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Pet   | turtle  | guinea-pig | ferret      | horse  | hedgehog | snake |
| Sport     | basketball | baseball  | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling  | sailing    |

