.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
There are 6 different nationalities: chinese, turkish, russian, french, pakistani, italian
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, banana, avocado, corn, mango, spinach
 1. the person eating avocado is the chinese##1
 2. the turkish is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 3. the person eating mango is on the left of the russian##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the turkish##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 7. the italian is on the right of the french##1
 8. the chinese is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 9. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the french is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Nationality         | french | italian | chinese | pakistani | turkish | russian  |
| Food   | spinach  | corn  | avocado  | broccoli | mango      | banana |

