.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
House: wooden, townhouse, victorian, art-deco, tower, futuristic
The people use 6 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, skateboard, van, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the person driving the van is the futuristic house##1
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
8. the tower house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
9. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| House   | futuristic    | victorian    | wooden | tower     | townhouse   | art-deco     |
| Transport   | van | scooter | helicopter | subway | skateboard | quad-bike |

