.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, cain, blend, bolivar, oliveros
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, woodworking, video-games, traveling, board-games, drawing
1. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the blend-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Cigar   | oliveros | tiparillo  | bolivar     | cain    | game  | blend          |
| Hobby         | woodworking  | collecting | video-games | board-games | traveling | drawing |

