.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, camping, photography, video-games, collecting
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: disco, reggae, funk, metal, ambient, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
4. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of metal##1
8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Hobby   | collecting    | puzzles     | camping | writing | photography | video-games   |
| Music-Genre        | hip-hop | metal | ambient | funk   | disco    | reggae |

