.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, rose, bellflower, tulip, iris
City: boston, liverpool, prague, edinburgh, marseilles, miami
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
9. the person who growsiris is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Flower         | rose | balloon-flower | tulip | bellflower | begonia    | iris |
| City   | boston   | marseilles      | edinburgh        | prague    | liverpool | miami  |

